{"tid":2508893,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"東北要人！！古洞貓狗需要你","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T05:53:13.000Z","uid":398233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"382cc19d168df6ebde94a30fcc962aaa334d6c92","tid":2508893,"uid":398233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"東北遷拆 好多人因為上左公屋 冇能力/唔想帶走 <br />\n留低左好多貓狗 人去樓空 靠留低既村民幫手餵 但冇人幫手絕育 係咁生 <br />\n依家漁護署成日都入去捉貓狗 人道毁滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毛孩守護者都有出過手 但狗場已經爆滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以睇下d 義工 fb page for 相關資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NENTAnimalRangers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNENTAnimalRangers&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNza0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=f4bba3ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NENTAnimalRangers</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/834799400045107/user/100007107253406 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F834799400045107%2Fuser%2F100007107253406%20&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNza0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=ad16536c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/834799400045107/user/100007107253406 </a><br />\n<br />\n知道咁多隻貓狗要幫到哂係好唔實際<br />\n但希望盡力幫佢地搵到人收養同暫託 同埋組隊幫手捉佢地絕育先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但長遠係需要極大量暫託/領養 <br />\n希望有巴絲可以一齊諗計 個到義工暫時得幾個 <br />\n我打算整d 文宣懶人包 翻譯<br />\n<br />\ntg: ＠meowmeowwoofwoof<br />\n<br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f47ff54b9a5c7095fda15ee9c0384d9ae2388f0","tid":2508893,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"76d525ce62f53c60e8e95c644540d88632c22eea","tid":2508893,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲資訊可唔可以唔好淨係得fb一個sources <br />\n好多人已經完全冇用fb<br />\n見到都唔知入唔入去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79648c389312d27c7670491adddb0b1abaca5ed","tid":2508893,"uid":398233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d525ce62f53c60e8e95c644540d88632c22eea","tid":2508893,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲資訊可唔可以唔好淨係得fb一個sources <br />\n好多人已經完全冇用fb<br />\n見到都唔知入唔入去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太忙 未有時間整理 <br />\n好多義工仲用緊 fb <br />\n會盡快整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf92d7f87387e59c42247793aae22267f072193b","tid":2508893,"uid":291921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f84adbca243f612d14141ee816959f6cb7c6de5d","tid":2508893,"uid":108816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"想領養嘅人可以諗諗 PUSH"}]}